name: Samsung Galaxy Note8
description: The new Galaxy Note8 and AT&T unleash your potential to create and enjoy. Do bigger things with Samsung's latest Infinity Display, smart S Pen, world's first Dual Camera with Optical Image Stabilization on both lenses, and the power of the AT&T network.

name: Samsung Galaxy S8
description: Imagine a phone with a world inside it. It opens when it sees your face, learns from you and erases barriers between you and the world on a massive, beautiful Infinity Screen. The new Galaxy S8 frees you to live every part of your life almost anywhere.

name: Samsung Galaxy S8 Active
description: Because the Samsung Galaxy S8 Active is durable on the outside with a long-lasting battery on the inside, you won't have to compromise one pixel of entertainment.

name: Moto Z2 Force Edition
description: The Moto Z2 Force Edition(TM) transforms your connection to the world of entertainment. Enjoy cool new capabilities with Moto Mods(TM). And with the built-in DIRECTV NOW App, you can watch your favorite movies and shows virtually anywhere.

name: LG G6
description: The LG G6 makes mobile viewing entertaining with immersive Dolby Vision and an 18:9 FullVision QHD+ display, and it can still fit in your hand.

name: LG X venture
description: The LG X venture(TM) is built for the unexpected with an IP68 rating2 for water/dust resistance, and it passed 14 military-standard 810G tests.1 The 4100mAh battery gives you plenty of power for life's adventures and entertainment on the go. Only at AT&T.

name: LG K20
description: When life demands bigger perspective, the LG K20(TM) delivers technology and value. Watch TV and movies on the big 5.3" HD screen. Take great photos with the 5 MP auto shot selfie camera. And access your phone and its contents with the fingerprint sensor.

name: Samsung Galaxy J7 (2017)
description: Samsung Galaxy J7 (2017) 5.5" HD display is ideal for streaming movies and connecting with friends. The 8 MP camera captures clear photos. And it can store thousands of photos (based on 2MB per picture)-at a price that is truly amazing.

name: Apple iPhone X
description: iPhone X. You've never seen anything like it. It's never seen anything like you.

displayContentItems.description: Get up to $300 in credits when you trade in your iPhone 7 Plus, or up to $200 in credits on other select devices.

name: Apple iPhone 8
description: iPhone 8 is a new generation of iPhone. Designed with the most durable glass ever in a smartphone and a stronger aerospace grade aluminum band. Charges wirelessly. Resists water and dust. 4.7-inch Retina HD display with True Tone.

displayContentItems.description: Get up to $300 in credits when you trade in your iPhone 7 Plus, or up to $200 in credits on other select devices.

name: Apple iPhone 8 Plus
description: iPhone 8 Plus is a new generation of iPhone. Designed with the most durable glass ever in a smartphone and a stronger aerospace grade aluminum band. Charges wirelessly. Resists water and dust. 5.5-inch Retina HD display with True Tone.

displayContentItems.description: Get up to $300 in credits when you trade in your iPhone 7 Plus, or up to $200 in credits on other select devices.

name: Apple iPhone 7
description: An entirely new camera system. The brightest, most colorful iPhone display ever. The fastest performance and best battery life in an iPhone. Every bit as powerful as it looks-this is iPhone 7.

name: Apple iPhone 7 Plus
description: All-new dual 12 MP cameras. The brightest, most colorful iPhone display ever. The fastest performance and best battery life in an iPhone. And stereo speakers. Every bit as powerful as it looks-this is iPhone 7 Plus.

name: Apple iPhone 6s Plus
description: With 3D Touch, Live Photos, 7000 series aluminum, A9 chip, advanced cameras, 5.5-inch Retina HD display, and so much more, you'll see how with iPhone 6s Plus the only thing that's changed is everything.

name: Apple iPhone 6s
description: With 3D Touch, Live Photos, 7000 series aluminum, A9 chip, advanced cameras, 4.7-inch Retina HD display, and so much more, youll see how with iPhone 6s the only thing thats changed is everything.

name: Samsung Gear S2
description: With elegant curves and premium finishes, the Samsung Gear S2 will turn heads. The intuitive circular face and bezel let you navigate effortlessly to get to what you need. Get more out of the moments in your day with Samsung Gear S2 and AT&T network.

name: LG B470
description: A flip phone crafted for your convenience, delivering functionality and accessibility with dedicated quick access function buttons, enhanced audio (senior) mode and audible text to speech messaging.

name: AT&T Cingular Flip 2
description: The AT&T Cingular Flip(TM) 2, exclusively at AT&T, includes a large keypad and display to easily navigate the icon-based menu. Surf the web using a fast 4G LTE or Wi-Fi connection and enjoy crystal clear calls with HD Voice.

name: Kyocera DuraXE
description: Whether you're working in tough conditions, an outdoor enthusiast, or just want a simple rugged phone, DuraXE offers all the features to get the job done. With EPTT, superior audio, and a 5 MP camera, you can stay productive in virtually any environment.

name: Apple iPhone SE
description: iPhone SE features a 4-inch Retina display, an A9 chip with 64-bit desktop-class architecture, the Touch ID fingerprint sensor, a 12MP iSight camera, a FaceTime HD camera with Retina Flash, Live Photos, iOS 9, and iCloud.

name: Samsung Gear S3 classic
description: Leave your phone behind with a 4G LTE connected Gear S3 classic. Call and text, check and send emails, schedule DIRECTV recordings and change channels, track fitness and moreall from your wrist on the nations best data network.

name: LG V30
description: Watch live and recorded TV shows on the LG V30(TM) 6-inch FullVision(TM) QHD+ OLED display. Create high-quality videos with expanded color and clarity, dramatic pinpoint zooming, and Hi-Fi audio that can be edited and shared right from your phone.

name: Axon M
description: Dual screens. Unlimited potential. Let AT&T and the ZTE Axon M(TM) open a world of simultaneous messaging, gaming, and unlimited streaming entertainment for you. Two-screen viewing you can hold in one hand allows for true multitasking.

name: KEYone
description: Everything you expect from BlackBerry®, now in an Android(TM) smartphone. Security, stunning photographs, powerful battery, a reimagined keyboard, and the full ecosystem of Android apps deliver a truly modern mobile experience.

name: Samsung Galaxy S7
description: Slim, sleek, and packed with power, the Samsung Galaxy S7 shows an amazing picture on a Quad HD Super AMOLED display. Plus, with DIRECTV integration, you can watch live TV, movies, and recorded shows anytime, anywhere.

name: Kyocera DuraForce PRO
description: No other smartphone offers a combination of rugged, security and lifestyle features. The KYOCERA DuraForce PRO is designed and built for people who play hard and work harder. Dont do rugged like an amateur. Do rugged like a pro.

name: Sonim XP5
description: The Sonim XP5® is an ultra-rugged LTE Wi-Fi device that's EPTT capable, water-, dust-, and drop-proof. It includes an extra-loud speaker and a powerful battery-all backed by a comprehensive 3-year warranty.

name: LG Watch Sport (AT&T Certified Restored)
description: The LG Watch Sport connected smartwatch offers a perfect balance of timepiece, health and fitness tracker, and independent wireless connectivity. Leave your phone behind, but take your world with you
